org.chronos.chronodb.internal.impl.mapdb

Class MapDBTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chronos.chronodb.internal.impl.mapdb.MapDBTransaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class MapDBTransaction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    A very thin wrapper around DB that implements AutoCloseable for convenience.

    All other methods are just forwarded to the wrapped instance.
